# RepoSage Ignore File
# Add file/directory patterns to exclude from analysis.
# Syntax follows .gitignore-like conventions:
#   - `dir/`        excludes an entire directory
#   - `*.ext`       excludes all files with a given extension
#   - `path/file`   excludes a specific file
#   - `subdir/*`    excludes all files directly under subdir
# Lines starting with # are comments.

# Examples:
# vendor/
# *.min.js
# docs/generated/
# tests/fixtures/
